OMG Mariah loved seeing all these artists and celebrities doing this video. No offense to Bing Crosby but I think your cover of this song is giving it a run for the money for becoming the all time classic Christmas song in America. Loved seeing Katy Perry(She should have gotten Orlando to do it with her too. :) ) and my own LAS VEGAS GOLDEN KNIGHTS hockey team. YEA!! And saw John Travolta in there also which was fun. Anytime I am feeling sad or depressed this song can ALWAYS cheer me up. I have ADD, Liver Disease, and Cancer now so I need as much cheering up as I can get and this is one of the best songs to me for doing that. I hope you had a wonderful Christmas Mariah and hope you have many more in the future.



Thanks for all the happy memories. :)
